snippet.title: The Quiet Things | First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into Alice's world in the debut trailer for The Quiet Things 📽️

Based on a true story, this narrative game takes a bold look at mental health using real diary entries 📖

From BAFTA Breakthrough Alyx Jones & Team, feat. the voice talent of Lorraine Ansell, Elsie Oliver, Emily Burnett & Dave Jones, with music by Alyx Jones. Kickstarter coming soon!
